[Stage Modifier]
author=BigBossman
description=When a Destruction Bowl Stage has been designated when playing a wrecking race, the Wrecking Racing stage that you chose will load normally. When designating a Wrecking Racing stage while playing on Destruction Bowl mode, the Wrecking Racing track will appear. This doesn't work on Championship Mode.
Values - 
00 - Airfield
01 - Chinatown
02 - Steelworks
03 - Casino
04 - Harbor
05 - South Central
06 - Under Construction
07 - Chinatown 2
08 - Refinery
09 - South Central 2
0A - Subway
0B - Casino 2
0C - The Dam
0D - B-Movie
0E - Colosseum
0F - Redline
10 - Titan
11 - Rough Justice
